&lt;li&gt;Strong familiarity with Edmonton streets and roadways.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Physical ability to lift up to 50 pounds and perform tasks requiring stooping, bending, walking, and standing for extended periods.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
